text: Anastasia Borisovna Kocherzhova (; born 16 October 1990) is a Russian bobsledder. She competed in the two-woman event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Russia Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
